column2: SELECT b.ra, b.dec, sp.teffadop, sp.fehadop, sp.loggadop, sp.snr, sp.flag into mydb.cross_param from mydb.MyTable as b CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (b.ra, b.dec, #) as c join DR1#.specobjall as so on so.bestobjid = c.objid JOIN sppparams sp ON so.specobjid = sp.specobjid and so.sciencePrimary = #
